#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
BrainChat ADV v4 (Offline) — Tkinter + Ollama + Self-Dialogue Engine (SABLE)

What this is:
- A fast offline chat UI (Tkinter) that talks to local Ollama (/api/chat)
- Adds a **self-dialogue pipeline** (draft -> critique -> final) to improve quality
- Uses **controlled meta-awareness** (precision mode switching) WITHOUT "I am a model" cringe
- Optional **Safety Lens**: warns (doesn't block) when content looks risky

Design goals:
- Keep ADV v3 performance wins (single queue pump, session logging, streaming cancel)
- Only stream the FINAL pass (draft/critique are quick non-stream calls)
- Zero extra deps beyond: python3, requests

Run:
  python3 brainchat_v4.py
"""

